<TITLE> Debapriya appointed ambassador to UN Offices in Geneva </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Sept 20 (bdnews24.com) -- The government has appointed Dr Debapriya Bhattacharya as Bangladesh's ambassador and permanent representative to the UN Offices in Geneva. The foreign ministry released a statement Thursday on the appointment of Debapriya, who is currently working for a nongovernmental think-tank, Centre for Policy Dialogue, as executive director. bdn
